<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About Parkview Weather</h1>
<p class="mb-4">Welcome to Parkview Weather! This application provides information about various national parks including current weather conditions and maps.</p>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Data Sources</h2>
<ul class="list-disc list-inside">
  <li class="mb-2">
    <strong>National Park Service (NPS) API</strong>
    <p>Provides data on parks including their names, descriptions, locations, and images.</p>
  </li>
  <li class="mb-2">
    <strong>OpenWeatherMap API</strong>
    <p>Offers weather data including current conditions and forecasts for the parks.</p>
  </li>
  <li class="mb-2">
    <strong>Mapbox API</strong>
    <p>Provides maps and geolocation data for the parks.</p>
  </li>
</ul>
